<refnamediv><refname>imrange</refname><refpurpose>Return image intensity range.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>value = imrange(image)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv><refsection><title>Parameters</title><variablelist><varlistentry><term>image</term><listitem><para>Input image or numeric array.</para></listitem></varlistentry><varlistentry><term>value</term><listitem><para>Difference between the maximum and minimum values.</para></listitem></varlistentry></variablelist></refsection>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>imrange</function> returns max(image(:)) - min(image(:)).</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting><![CDATA[image = imread(fullpath(getIPCVpath() + "/images/opencv_left01.jpg"));
image = imresize(rgb2gray(image), [120 160]);
value = imrange(image);
disp(value);
imshow(image);]]></programlisting></refsection>
